channel.title: 317 RSPS offline
channel.description: Hey guys I'm looking for a RSPS I can quickly download, change the JDK and run it working properly. My roommate and I are getting bored of other games and we just want to play a RSPS by ourselves. The only thing we're picky about is just we want a new(er) interface like when the emotes are pictures, not words. This is not a must, but if you also come across one with newer items such as torva, virtus, etc, I'd like that. We don't get enough internet time to search for awhile so that's why I'm asking. I do not plan on leeching and calling it my own, just want to play it offline with a friend.
